## 2. Dashboard Cards

### Railnova Metric Cards
**Source:** `railnova-operational-dashboard-guide.png`

**Pattern Analysis:**

| Element | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Layout** | Grid of cards, 3-4 per row |
| **Content** | Metric name, value, optional trend |
| **Interaction** | Click to drill down |

**What Works:**
- Clean white cards on dark sidebar
- Numbers prominent, labels secondary
- Grouping by category

**What Doesn't Work:**
- Dense information may overwhelm new users

**Recommendation for MMS-MFC:**
```
COPY: Card grid layout
ADAPT: Use Blueprint.js Card component
ADD: Trend indicators (up/down arrows)
```

