## 5. Map Components

### Railnova Map View
**Source:** `railnova-map-features.png`

![Railnova Map](../images/competitive-research/railnova-map-features.png)

**Pattern Analysis:**

| Element | Implementation |
|---------|----------------|
| **Base map** | Dark or satellite imagery |
| **Markers** | Colored pins for assets |
| **Clustering** | Groups nearby markers |
| **Popups** | Asset info on click |
| **Filters** | Sidebar or top bar |

**What Works:**
- Status-colored markers match dashboard
- Cluster groups prevent clutter
- Real-time position updates
- Route/track visualization

**What Doesn't Work:**
- May lag with many assets
- Mobile interaction can be tricky

**Recommendation for MMS-MFC:**
```
COPY: Status-colored markers
COPY: Clustering for density management
ADD: Filter by status, depot, type
ADD: Click marker to see asset detail sidebar
```

